subSubSection.paragraph:
Distribution and natural history : The currently known, vast distribution ranges from Nepal , India , and Sri Lanka across South China , Thailand , Laos , and Vietnam eastwards to South Japan and southeastwards to Indonesia ( Sumatra , Java , Lombok, Bali ) ( Map 6 ); for previous records see ASSING (2016a) (as
Z. hongkongensis
). The specimens known at present were collected at low altitudes, primarily at light sources.
